        <div class="row">
            
    <article>
        <h1>Technology</h1>
        <h2>A breakthrough in<br>chemical innovation</h2>
        <p>Simplot ingenuity and advanced technology came together to create F<span class="umacr">&#362;</span>SN&trade;, a safe ammonium nitrate fertilizer. Using advanced engineering and manufacturing expertise, Simplot fused ammonium nitrate with ammonium sulfate to produce a new fused molecule that is less detonable and better delivers dual ammonium nitrate nutrients to the plant.</p>

        <p>In its simplest form, the F<span class="umacr">&#362;</span>SN technology fuses ammonium nitrate (a potent fertilizer) with ammonium sulfate (a natural suppressing fertilizer) to produce a 3-to-1 &ldquo;double salt&rdquo; matrix with two AN molecules for each AS molecule. By chemically fusing a fertilizer with a fertilizer, Simplot can offer a better, safer and more advanced ammonium nitrate fertilizer.</p>
    </article>

        </div>
    </div>

